data.description: Welcome Home!! Looking for Space Inside and Out, Look No Further. This Beautiful Home is Situated on a Large Corner Lot with Encapsulated Crawl Space. This Hard To Come by layout offers, a foyer, a Great Room with Fireplace, Formal Living Room, Sunroom and a Sizeable Backyard, Custom Kitchen with large breakfast area, Granite Counter-Tops, Under Cabinet Lighting, Updated Appliances, Finished Basement, Two Guest Bedrooms One With Private Bath, Large Owners Suite with Relaxing ensuite, as Well as a Third Bathroom All on the Main Level! There are Two Large Bedrooms, Two Full Baths, Loft Retreat for Reading and/or Home Office Situated on the 2nd floor and 2 car garage. VA Assumable Loan @ 2.75%!
